{"tid":2302121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通識課時減半，只設合格、不合格   楊潤雄：差不多","createTime":"2020-11-27T01:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T02:31:17.000Z","uid":44428,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e806ddec6bc1de2d771abc4ffe75366a6c8bb8ee","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"係啦所有嘢都係差唔多啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2368173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Flocal%2F2368173&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=5ba00e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2368173</a>"},{"pid":"234c8405579a5365d273b4cc8d156917c499922d","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"你知道中國最有名的人是誰？提起此人，人人皆曉，處處聞名，他姓差，名不多，是各省各縣各村人氏。你一定見過他，一定聽過別人談起他，差不多先生的名字，天天掛在大家的口頭，因為他是中國全國人的代表。"},{"pid":"93e7a4d40a576c5ad4b3f368ff61c2d964ba2e73","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"他常常說：「凡事只要差不多，就好了。何必太精明呢？」<br />\n<br />\n他小時候，他媽叫他去買紅糖，他買了白糖回來，他媽罵他，他搖搖頭道：「紅糖，白糖，不是差不多嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n他在學堂的時候，先生問他：「直隸省的西邊是哪一省？」他說是陝西。先生說：「錯了，是山西，不是陝西。」他說：「陝西同山西，不是差不多嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n後來他在一個錢鋪裏做夥計；他也會寫，也會算，只是總不會精細；十字常常寫成千字，千字常常寫成十字。掌櫃的生氣了，常常罵他，他只笑嘻嘻地賠小心道：「千字比十字多一小撇，不是差不多嗎？」"},{"pid":"4496a2ffecd24108ab99f4cdb79dec5232fb243c","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:23:14.000Z","msg":"有一天，他忽然得一急病，趕快叫家人去請東街的汪先生。那家人急急忙忙跑去，一時尋不著東街的汪大夫，卻把西街的牛醫王大夫請來了。差不多先生病在上，知道尋錯了人；但病急了，身上痛苦，心裏焦急，等不得了，心裏想道：「好在王大夫同汪大夫也差不多，讓他試試看罷。」於是這位牛醫王大夫走近前，用醫牛的法子給差不多先生治病。不上一點鐘，差不多先生就一命嗚呼了。<br />\n<br />\n差不多先生差不多要死的時候，一口氣斷斷續續地說道：「活人同死人也差&hellip;&hellip;差&hellip;&hellip;差&hellip;&hellip;不多，&hellip;&hellip;凡事只要&hellip;&hellip;差&hellip;&hellip;差&hellip;&hellip;不多&hellip;&hellip;就&hellip;&hellip;好了，何&hellip;&hellip;必&hellip;&hellip;太&hellip;&hellip;太認真呢？」他說完了這句格言，就絕了氣。"},{"pid":"30fa508e3eb0b3ac88198c26fc4d725b40592233","tid":2302121,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"差不多香港 差不多教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只設合格不合格姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛國合格"},{"pid":"39378626dfe3304b759c8ab63dd2e288456f910f","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f639119a31cbbaddd6bbeecc64fe51d0df94d8","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"楊差不多會計師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjHSOzt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjHSOzt.png&h=494dc3c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0adf240cb15d292e4266d625b67439a222df4733","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差唔多啫，以後就叫佢差不多先生"},{"pid":"ed50ed6d959e5a9960009a4be4edd48bebe94fa1","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e0d966445a496ac69ded39df6a4b35471ae5b0","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e884183f568d77e3c19d8103203e3d6b678a535","tid":2302121,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}